    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "FTFWN",
      "x": -600,
      "y": 8200,
      "name": "Documentation",
      "width": 1200,
      "fill": "#FFFFFF",
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 40,
      "padding": 40,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "3PxUN",
          "name": "docTitle",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "content": "TRADEX — Design Documentation",
          "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
          "fontSize": 32,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "xNc97",
          "name": "docSubtitle",
          "fill": "#555555",
          "content": "Component Tree · Interaction & State Transitions · Design System Specification",
          "fontFamily": "Inter",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "rectangle",
          "id": "H7tpi",
          "name": "divider1",
          "fill": "#D1CCC4",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "height": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "BylnQ",
          "name": "sec1Title",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "content": "1. Component Tree",
          "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
          "fontSize": 24,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "VqFLv",
          "name": "sec1Body",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Buttons\n├─ Button/Primary (KiPSY) — Dark bg, light text. Used for primary actions (Report, Execute).\n│   └─ icon (icon_font, lucide) + label (text)\n├─ Button/Secondary (8YupF) — Card-bg, dark text. Used for filter, back navigation.\n│   └─ icon (icon_font) + label (text)\n├─ Button/Accent (NVezV) — Terracotta bg (#C05A3C). Used for sign-in, sign-up CTAs.\n│   └─ icon (icon_font) + label (text)\n├─ Button/Danger (7momf) — Red bg (#B54A4A). Used for sell, destructive actions.\n│   └─ icon (icon_font) + label (text)\n└─ Button/Ghost (baZfW) — Transparent, dark text. Used for secondary links.\n    └─ icon (icon_font) + label (text)",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "tlzgi",
          "name": "sec1Body2",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Form\n└─ InputGroup (XQuC5) — Vertical stack: label + field frame.\n    ├─ label (text) — Uppercase, 10px, tertiary\n    └─ field (frame) — Card bg, border-light stroke\n        ├─ icon (icon_font, lucide)\n        └─ placeholder (text)",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "3QB0q",
          "name": "sec1Body3",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Status Badges\n├─ Badge/Queued (RIJqP) — bg-card, border-light stroke. Marker: text-tertiary.\n├─ Badge/Running (Tlf7r) — info bg (#5C7C8A). Marker: white.\n├─ Badge/Completed (o2vL1) — success bg (#4A7C59). Marker: white.\n└─ Badge/Failed (OKCZD) — error bg (#B54A4A). Marker: white.\n    Each: marker (rectangle 8×8) + label (text, 9px uppercase)",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "lwKdv",
          "name": "sec1Body4",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Navigation\n├─ NavItem/Active (1Dx4H) — Accent left border, accent icon+text.\n│   └─ icon (icon_font) + label (text)\n├─ NavItem/Default (CaOj1) — Transparent, muted icon+text.\n│   └─ icon (icon_font) + label (text)\n└─ Sidebar (pUOAe) — Full-height dark bg frame.\n    ├─ top: logo section (icon + text)\n    ├─ nav slot (tjRKv): Accepts NavItem instances\n    └─ bottom: user avatar section",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "PuMCk",
          "name": "sec1Body5",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Data Display\n├─ Table/HeaderRow (xx6vT) — Horizontal frame of HeaderCells.\n│   └─ HeaderCell (bER9w): frame + text (10px, uppercase, tertiary)\n├─ Table/Row (Hu6HE) — Horizontal frame of Cells, border-bottom stroke.\n│   └─ Cell (3GCcW): frame + text (12px, primary)\n├─ ChangeIndicator/Up (mB69y) — Green: arrow-up icon + percentage text.\n└─ ChangeIndicator/Down (EgeO9) — Red: arrow-down icon + percentage text.",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "qxF61",
          "name": "sec1Body6",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Screen Structure\n├─ Login (jofpS) — 1440×900, horizontal split\n│   ├─ BrandPanel (dark, fill_container): logo + hero text + footer\n│   └─ FormPanel (520px, bg-page): title + 2 InputGroups + Accent button + link\n├─ Sign Up (VpVzU) — Same layout, 4 InputGroups + Accent button\n├─ Screening Main (MMpvV) — Sidebar + content area\n│   ├─ Sidebar: nav items (Screening/Reports/Orders/Settings)\n│   └─ Content: header + table (7 cols) + right panel (360px)\n│       ├─ Report Status: 4 badge items (queued/running/completed/failed)\n│       └─ Quick Order: Buy/Sell tabs + Qty/Price/Total fields + Execute\n├─ Report Detail (nPxiZ) — Sidebar + content\n│   ├─ Left: Analysis card + 4 metric cards + Technical table\n│   └─ Right: Quick Actions (Buy/Sell) + Signal Strength card\n├─ Error States\n│   ├─ Login Failed (MziDt): Login layout + red error banner\n│   ├─ Session Expired (RNf1N): Modal overlay + timer icon + re-auth CTA\n│   └─ Unauthorized (WY3tE): Modal overlay + shield icon + Go Back/Sign In\n└─ Mobile\n    ├─ Mobile Login (Kf64T): 390×844, vertical: dark header + form below\n    └─ Mobile Screening (b4bGx): 390×844, top bar + card list + bottom tabs",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "rectangle",
          "id": "PvO2W",
          "name": "divider2",
          "fill": "#D1CCC4",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "height": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "oM2IW",
          "name": "sec2Title",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "content": "2. Interaction & State Transitions",
          "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
          "fontSize": 24,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "CQ1y8",
          "name": "sec2Auth",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Authentication Flow\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n[Login Page] ──── valid credentials ───→ [Screening Main]\n     │                                         │\n     ├── invalid credentials ───→ [Login Failed State]\n     │         └── dismiss banner → [Login Page]\n     │\n     └── \"Sign up\" link ───→ [Sign Up Page]\n                                   │\n                           submit ──→ [Login Page]\n\n[Any Authenticated Page]\n     ├── token expired ───→ [Session Expired Modal]\n     │         └── \"Sign In Again\" → [Login Page]\n     │\n     └── insufficient permissions ───→ [Unauthorized Modal]\n               ├── \"Go Back\" → previous page\n               └── \"Sign In\" → [Login Page]",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "J5e4s",
          "name": "sec2Screen",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Screening Table Interactions\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n• Manual Refresh: Click refresh button → loading spinner → table data updates\n  - Data cached for 5min premise; button shows cooldown state if < 5min\n• Sort: Click column header → toggle asc/desc sort on that column\n• Filter: Click FILTER button → filter panel slides down\n  - Market dropdown, RSI range, Volume min, Change % range\n  - Apply → table filtered; Reset → show all\n• Report Generation: Click REPORT on any row\n  → Badge: Queued → Running → Completed/Failed\n  - OpenClaw MCP generates report; poll status every 3s\n  - Completed → click to open Report Detail view\n  - Failed → show error toast + retry option\n  - Results cached in Redis for 1h (model_name excluded from UI)",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "8gEZy",
          "name": "sec2Order",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Quick Order Panel\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n• Tab Selection: Buy (default) / Sell\n  - Buy tab → green accent on Execute button\n  - Sell tab → red accent on Execute button\n• Fields: Quantity (number input), Price (number input)\n  - Total auto-calculates: Qty × Price\n• Execute: Click → confirmation dialog → API call → success/error toast\n• Row Selection: Clicking a stock row in the table pre-fills symbol + price\n\nReport Detail Interactions\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\n• Back button → returns to Screening Main\n• Quick Actions: Buy/Sell → opens Quick Order pre-filled with stock data\n• Signal Strength: Visual score (0-100) + sentiment label (BULLISH/BEARISH/NEUTRAL)\n• Metric cards: Display latest RSI, 24H Change, Volume, Price",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "gmmbh",
          "name": "sec2Nav",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Navigation State Map\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nDesktop (Sidebar)              Mobile (Bottom Tabs)\n┌─────────────┐                ┌────────────────────┐\n│ Screening ● │ active         │ Screening ● │ active\n│ Reports     │ → detail view  │ Reports     │\n│ Orders      │ → order history│ Orders      │\n│ Settings    │ → preferences  │ Settings    │\n└─────────────┘                └────────────────────┘\n● = accent color, others = text-tertiary\nSidebar collapses to icons at < 1024px viewport",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "rectangle",
          "id": "wPzTC",
          "name": "divider3",
          "fill": "#D1CCC4",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "height": 2
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "8JyzS",
          "name": "sec3Title",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "content": "3. Design System Specification",
          "fontFamily": "Space Grotesk",
          "fontSize": 24,
          "fontWeight": "700"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "m2YDd",
          "name": "sec3Style",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Style: Nordic Brutalist\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nSharp geometric forms, 0px corner radius throughout, warm muted\npalette with terracotta accent, monospace data displays, strong\ntypographic hierarchy. High contrast dark/light split layouts.",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "Jvbsa",
          "name": "sec3Colors",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Color Tokens (Design Variables)\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nBackgrounds                    Text\n  bg-page      #F5F3EF          text-primary    #1A1A1A\n  bg-sidebar   #1A1A1A          text-secondary  #555555\n  bg-card      #E8E4DC          text-tertiary   #888888\n  bg-dark      #1A1A1A          text-muted      #666666\n  bg-dark-surface #2A2A2A       text-light      #F5F3EF\n  bg-dark-subtle  #3A3A3A\n\nSemantic                       Borders\n  accent       #C05A3C            border-light  #D1CCC4\n  success      #4A7C59            border-dark   #3A3A3A\n  warning      #C05A3C\n  error        #B54A4A          Trading\n  info         #5C7C8A            buy-green     #4A7C59\n                                  sell-red      #B54A4A",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "qfWVK",
          "name": "sec3Type",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Typography\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nFont Stack:\n  Headings & UI:  Space Grotesk (700, 600)\n  Body & Labels:  Inter (400, 500)\n  Data/Code:      IBM Plex Mono (500)\n\nScale:\n  Hero title     28-32px  Space Grotesk 700\n  Section title  22-24px  Space Grotesk 700\n  Card title     16-18px  Space Grotesk 600\n  Body text      13-14px  Inter 400\n  Table data     12px     Space Grotesk 600\n  Labels         10-11px  Space Grotesk 600, uppercase, letter-spacing: 1px\n  Badge text     9px      Space Grotesk 600, uppercase\n  Small caption  9-10px   Space Grotesk 500",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "q4Jv2",
          "name": "sec3Spacing",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Spacing & Layout\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nCorner Radius:  0px everywhere (Nordic Brutalist principle)\n\nSpacing Scale:\n  4px   — tight (icon-to-label gap in badges)\n  6px   — compact (button icon-to-label)\n  8px   — small (logo mark-to-text, nav icon-to-label)\n  12px  — medium (card internal gap, panel sections)\n  16px  — standard (card padding, content gap, field gaps)\n  20px  — section gap (sidebar nav items)\n  24px  — large (content area gap)\n  32px  — container padding (main content areas)\n  40px  — extra-large (form section padding)\n\nLayout Grid:\n  Desktop: 1440×900\n    Sidebar: 220px fixed\n    Content: fill_container\n    Right panel: 360px (Screening), or 2-column split (Report)\n  Mobile: 390×844\n    Top bar: 56px height\n    Bottom nav: 60px height\n    Content padding: 16px\n    Cards replace tables for data display",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "jHOrQ",
          "name": "sec3Icons",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Iconography\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nIcon Set:     Lucide (primary)\nDefault Size: 16×16px (UI), 14×14px (compact), 20×20px (mobile nav)\n\nUsage Map:\n  Navigation:   layout-dashboard, file-text, shopping-cart, settings\n  Actions:      refresh-cw, sliders-horizontal, plus, arrow-left\n  Auth:         mail, lock, user, log-in\n  Status:       triangle-alert, timer, shield-off\n  Trading:      arrow-up, arrow-down, file-text (report)\n  Data:         chart-bar, activity, trending-up\n\nIcon Color:\n  Active nav    → $accent\n  Default nav   → $text-muted\n  Button icon   → inherits button text color\n  Status icon   → inherits status color",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "Tk7sI",
          "name": "sec3States",
          "fill": "#1A1A1A",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Component States\n─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────\nButtons:\n  Default  → base colors as defined per variant\n  Hover    → 10% darker fill (CSS: brightness(0.9))\n  Active   → 15% darker fill\n  Disabled → 40% opacity\n\nInputs:\n  Default  → bg-card fill, border-light stroke (1px)\n  Focus    → border changes to accent (#C05A3C)\n  Error    → border changes to error (#B54A4A), error text below\n\nBadges (Report Status Lifecycle):\n  Queued    → bg-card, tertiary marker\n  Running   → info bg, animated pulse on marker\n  Completed → success bg, static marker\n  Failed    → error bg, static marker\n\nTable Rows:\n  Default  → transparent bg\n  Hover    → bg-card fill\n  Selected → accent border-left (2px)",
          "lineHeight": 1.8,
          "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
          "fontSize": 11,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
